Package com.cafean.client.ui.util

Interface Groupable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Annotation, DrawnSharedBoolean, DrawnSharedInteger, DrawnSharedReal, DrawnSharedString, DrawnSharedTable, DrawnUserValue, DrawnViewComponent, EllipticalAnnotation, ImageAnnotation, LineAnnotation, PolygonBean, RectangularAnnotation, TextAnnotation, VisualGroup
    public interface Groupable
    An interface that describes a visual component that can be part of a VisualGroup. Groupable objects a group id (the ident of the group) and a flag used to determine if the id must be reconnected via the group's "old ident" field.
    See Also:
    BeanBox.reconnectGroupIDs()
